Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:14.97,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:34.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:03.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:15.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:18.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:24.73,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,200.389)}The Deadly Ice Devil
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:24.73,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs215\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,740.389)}Todogiller
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.26,0:01:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Send it my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Goro,\Nstop being such a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's it!\N - What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Children should play!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's decided!\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:01:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots. Keep it in bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who gave you\Npermission to play here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sorry! Our ball went over there!\N- We'll be more careful in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave my land at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not allowed to play here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times must I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Our ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a mean man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shocker cyborg appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at Ichimonji\NHayato's panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The cyborg I designed personally
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is beginning to use\Nits terrifying power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, I'll make you an icicle,\Njust like that old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A fate worth looking\Nforward to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See that Operation: Ice is performed\Nat once, and just as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We must bring the humans\Nturned to ice back to our base,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and then modify them\Ninto Shocker cyborgs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You will move on to this\Nstage of the plan at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The preparations\Nare all in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I will destroy Shocker's greatest\Nopposition, the Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then all that will remain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is to bring the humans\Nhere for modification.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:11.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Evil organization Shocker was\Nplotting to execute Operation: Ice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:13.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,using their new\Ncyborg, Todogiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:15.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But what exactly\Nis Operation: Ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty degrees to port!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The rudder's stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Another fishing boat was\Nsunk on its way back to port.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But that makes\Nseven since yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What caused it?\N An iceberg, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Each boat was in the middle of a\Ntelegraph about seeing a strange monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-A monster?\Nbut they were cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be that\Nmonster from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is,\Nthat means Shocker's behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to\Nthe boats' crews?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one man has been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... if Shocker's the\None sinking the boats,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker might be taking the\Ncrews, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's entirely possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Their families must\Nbe so worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those poor people...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Todogiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You must bring far\Nmore people than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We must perform surgery\Nto bring them back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and turn them into\NShocker cyborgs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we will turn Tokyo\Ninto a city of ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! I brought your medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You have homework, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can finish it next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's boat got sunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time for studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasuo...\Nyour father will come back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone at the harbor is saying
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:07:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no way to survive\Nhitting an iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're just mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So please...\Nplease, don't worry so much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If believing those rumors\Nforces you to stop studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It would just kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say stuff like that, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasuo, your father isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He would never die and leave\Nsuch a nice boy behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He will come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just believe that,\Nand wait for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's brought turmoil\Nto this quiet sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and sorrow to its\Npeople's peaceful lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You like the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate the ocean that\Ntook my dad away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father was\Ntaken by the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really waiting for\Nhim to come back, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy! Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, son. Stay close to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That Hayato...\Nhe's trying to get ahead of me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, I stuck a\Ntransmitter on his motorbike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape the\Neyes of Taki Kazuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!\NHow did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get them to tell us\Nwhere Shocker's hideout is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister! A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've shown yourself at\Nlast, Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can freeze all together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You wretched monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make this place your grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see now why Todogiller is\Nfeared, Ichimonji Hayato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Todogiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that perpetual thorn in our\Nside, the Kamen Rider is finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be no one\Nleft to stand against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I'll do\Nto the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My negative 300\Ndegree freezing shot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,will do the same thing\Nto the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Todogiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is\Ntrapped in the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:12:01.44,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think this\Nfire is hot enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki and Yasuo will\Ndie at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...\NI have only one choice left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:35.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider's idea was to heat\Nhis own body with the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:38.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and use that heat\Nto melt the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cold, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost out. Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Could there be another way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! You need your rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in the world\Nhave you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just about to send\Nthe police looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am. Please don't\Nbe so hard on Yasuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been waiting by the ocean,\Nworried about his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a friend of Yasuo's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasuo. Don't worry your\Nmother, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Todogiller,\Nit seems your plan has failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch. I won't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you all\Nhow Kamen Rider dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now his motorbike\Nwill slip on the ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him to our base!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the way\Nin to their base?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the great Kamen Rider is a helpless\Nice cube when frozen like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami,\Nlet me crush him while he's frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a far more\Ninteresting idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Defrost him, restart his heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,return him to his\NIchimonji Hayato form,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and then send him to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how Shocker\Nputs a man to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've caused Shocker\Nmuch grief in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But now,\Nit's your turn to suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You underestimated the power\Nof Kamen Rider, Todogiller!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I intentionally let myself get\Ncaptured to find a way into your base!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you holding the\Ncrew of the sunken boats?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you where they were!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hit Doctor Shinigami\Nwith your freezing shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll release them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Revive them all,\Nand return them to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it will be that easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Release Todogiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll return Taki to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go after Doctor Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Todogiller to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Todogiller!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape\Nus, Doctor Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Men like you sell your\Nsouls to the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow you to go free!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy Kamen Rider at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Face me, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The ice melted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank goodness!\N- We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Doctor Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And the frozen people?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I found them in the cave there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we\Ndidn't lose anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.05,0:22:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy! Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.55,0:22:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Yasuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Kamen Rider who saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice, Yasuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.35,0:22:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.66,0:22:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro, the Kamen Rider\Nsaved me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Hayato,\Nyou're so unreliable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.32,0:22:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:00.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider had put an end\Nto the ice devil Todogiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:04.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker had not given\Nup on world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.81,0:23:07.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What kind of cyborg would they\Ncreate to send at Kamen Rider next?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:10.59,Cont,,0,60,150,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:13.30,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:14.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:16.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Hiruguerrilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hiruguerrilla drinks the blood of\Nhumans and turns them into slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.26,0:23:25.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the most terrifying cyborg that\Ndastardly Shocker has created yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:27.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:30.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Hiruguerrilla of\Nthe Vampire Swamp!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:30.82,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(224,632)}Hiruguerrilla of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:30.82,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(644,718)}the Vampire Swamp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:40.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:43.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:48.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.57,0:23:50.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.44,0:23:52.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:54.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.11,0:23:55.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:57.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:03.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:07.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:10.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.35,0:24:15.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Deadly Ice\NDevil Todogiller